Jafar is A Framework for Algorithms development in Robotics.

Jafar is a development framework developed and used at LAAS. It adopts a
modular architecture which makes it easy for developers to plug-in their own
algorithms, and use algorithms developed by other people as well as core tools
providing a framework for display, documentation, unit tests, debug, etc. It
mainly relies on boost and opencv.

This packages provides basic image processing, it is based on the OpenCV
library.
